FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31220
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778785872
OL,3,CHow would a Labour leadership contest
OL,4,Cwork?
OL,6,FSomeone who has also been touted as a
OL,7,Fpotential contender is Armed Forces
OL,8,FMinister Al Carns.
OL,10,FCarns, a decorated ex-marine, has come
OL,11,Fout and said that voters deserve
OL,12,F"stability and fairness".
OL,14,FSeen as a candidate for the leadership
OL,15,Ffrom the more moderate wing of the
OL,16,Fparty, it has been reported that
OL,17,Fseveral MPs have been in touch with
OL,18,FCarns' allies and are convinced he may
OL,19,Frun, but only if Starmer were to stand
OL,20,Fdown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
